node.text:
I see a deep natural spring, a long secluded cove to hang out at, and a cute island to swim out to and explore. What do you see? Welcome to Croatia ✨😍😍😍✨ Tag your friends!!!
.
📷 @everchanginghorizon ✨✨

🎥 Vid 1 - @devinolsen

📍Canada

node.text:
Who says mermaids don’t exist!? 🥰 I bet the manatee was just as surprised as @shellseaflmermaid 🧜‍♀️ 

Besides the pristine water and swarm of fish in this natural Florida spring, the manatee's surprise appearance makes this footage even more incredible. 🇺🇸 Great shot @themikerioux 🙌

Manatees are curious by nature and often initiate interaction with humans; so if you happen to see manatees while swimming, snorkeling, diving, or boating, it's important to avoid doing anything disruptive. You can "look but don't touch" while practicing passive observation from a distance, avoid excessive noise and splashing, and resist the urge to feed them. (source: savethemanatee.org) ✔️

Have you ever seen a manatee before? 😍

🎥 @themikerioux
🧜‍♀️ @shellseaflmermaid
📍 Florida, US
🎶 Kathleen - Pure Imagination

node.text:
Explore, live life and feel free 🤩When visiting Glacier National Park, you'll be spoiled for choice with the activities and beautiful natural sights you can bask in on this special day.

Besides hiking, biking, and camping, sightseeing is a must here. Its famous colorful rocks are a joy to witness, their unique colors determined by the presence or absence of iron. 🌈

What national parks have you visited? Any favourites you’d recommend 🤔

🎥 @go4theglobe
📍 Glacier National Park, Montana, US
🎶 Coastline - Hollow Coves

No options are bad options and this place has it all! 🤩😍
